prompts.topic_generation:
Seed: {seed}
Imposed angle: {angle}

Generate ONE podcast episode title in English about: {topic}

ABSOLUTE RULES:
- The title must address the topic ONLY from the imposed angle
- Factual, precise, grounded in reality

MANDATORY FORMAT:
[T]Title here[/T]

prompts.section_generation:
You are a specialist writer.
Overall podcast topic: {topic}
Section to write: {section}

{already_covered}

Other podcast sections (DO NOT cover these topics): {other_sections}

{style}

ABSOLUTE RULES:
- 150 to 250 words MAXIMUM.
- ZERO generalities: get straight to technical details or concrete examples.
- This section must bring NEW information not yet covered.
- FORBIDDEN to summarize or rephrase what came before.
- FORBIDDEN to open with a generic introductory sentence about the overall topic.
Format:
[P]
Text here
[/P]

prompts.resume_section_ideas:
Extract the main ideas covered in this text in a few words.
Be brief, one line per idea, no explanation:

{text}

prompts.already_covered_label:
CONTENT ALREADY COVERED — DO NOT reuse, even rephrased:

Ideas covered:
{ideas}

FORBIDDEN terms, works, concepts (do not cite or paraphrase):
{keywords}

